    cmake,
    debhelper-compat (= 12),
    libglib2.0-dev,
    ofono-dev,
    ofono-sailfish-dev,
    ofono-ubports-dev,
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Section: libs
Homepage: http://gitlab.com/ubports/development/core/ofono-apndb-plugin
Vcs-Browser: http://gitlab.com/ubports/development/core/ofono-apndb-plugin
