Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: ofono-apndb-plugin
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
    ${shlibs:Depends},
    ${misc:Depends},
    ofono,
Conflicts:
    ofono-sailfish,
    ofono-ubports,
Recommends:
    lineageos-apndb,
Description: oFono apndb provisioning plugin - built against Sailfish fork
 Apndb is an XML format used by Android for their APN database. This plugin
 allows oFono to use such database.
 .
 This package is built against upstream variant of oFono.

